data_processing: Transcript-level abundance was quantified using Salmon v0.9.1 (Patro et al. Nature Methods, 2017) against the transcriptome for genome build GRCh37, Ensembl release 75.
data_processing.1: Gene-level abundances (counts and transcripts per million) were estimated using Tximport v0.99.8 (Soneson et al. 2015, F1000Research) using the ""lengthScaledTPM"" argument, and Ensembl transcript-to-Entrez gene ID cross references.
data_processing.3: Supplementary_files_format_and_content: csv files contain gene-level counts and transcript per million quantifications generated using tximport.
